{
    "poem_title": "SUR LA PAIX DE 1736",
    "author": "",
    "structure": "suite périodique",
    "year": "1709-1775",
    "manually_checked": false,
    "stanzas": [
        {
            "stanza_number": 1,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 1,
                    "line_text": "L'Etna renferme le tonnerre",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 2,
                    "line_text": "Dans ses épouvantables flancs ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 3,
                    "line_text": "Il vomit le feu sur la terre,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 4,
                    "line_text": "Il dévore ses habitants.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 5,
                    "line_text": "Fuyez, Dryades gémissantes,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 6,
                    "line_text": "Ces campagnes toujours brûlantes,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 7,
                    "line_text": "Ces abîmes toujours ouverts,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 8,
                    "line_text": "Ces torrents de flamme et de soufre,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "e"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 9,
                    "line_text": "Échappés du sein de ce gouffre",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "e"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 10,
                    "line_text": "Qui touche aux voûtes des enfers.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "L'Etna renferme le tonnerre\nDans ses épouvantables flancs ;\nIl vomit le feu sur la terre,\nIl dévore ses habitants.\nFuyez, Dryades gémissantes,\nCes campagnes toujours brûlantes,\nCes abîmes toujours ouverts,\nCes torrents de flamme et de soufre,\nÉchappés du sein de ce gouffre\nQui touche aux voûtes des enfers."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 2,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 11,
                    "line_text": "Plus terrible dans ses ravages,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 12,
                    "line_text": "Plus fier dans ses débordements,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 13,
                    "line_text": "Le Pô renverse ses rivages",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 14,
                    "line_text": "Cachés sous ses flots écumants :",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 15,
                    "line_text": "Avec lui marchent la Ruine,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 16,
                    "line_text": "L'Effroi, la Douleur, la Famine,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 17,
                    "line_text": "La Mort, les Désolations ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 18,
                    "line_text": "Et, dans les fanges de Ferrare,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "e"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 19,
                    "line_text": "Il entraîne à la mer avare",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "e"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 20,
                    "line_text": "Les dépouilles des nations.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Plus terrible dans ses ravages,\nPlus fier dans ses débordements,\nLe Pô renverse ses rivages\nCachés sous ses flots écumants :\nAvec lui marchent la Ruine,\nL'Effroi, la Douleur, la Famine,\nLa Mort, les Désolations ;\nEt, dans les fanges de Ferrare,\nIl entraîne à la mer avare\nLes dépouilles des nations."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 3,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 21,
                    "line_text": "Mais ces débordements de l'onde,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 22,
                    "line_text": "Et ces combats des éléments,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 23,
                    "line_text": "Et ces secousses qui du monde",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 24,
                    "line_text": "Ont ébranlé les fondements,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 25,
                    "line_text": "Fléaux que le ciel en colère",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 26,
                    "line_text": "Sur ce malheureux hémisphère",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 27,
                    "line_text": "A fait éclater tant de fois,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 28,
                    "line_text": "Sont moins affreux, sont moins sinistres,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "e"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 29,
                    "line_text": "Que l'ambition des ministres",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "e"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 30,
                    "line_text": "Et que les discordes des rois.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Mais ces débordements de l'onde,\nEt ces combats des éléments,\nEt ces secousses qui du monde\nOnt ébranlé les fondements,\nFléaux que le ciel en colère\nSur ce malheureux hémisphère\nA fait éclater tant de fois,\nSont moins affreux, sont moins sinistres,\nQue l'ambition des ministres\nEt que les discordes des rois."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 4,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 31,
                    "line_text": "De l'Inde aux bornes de la France,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 32,
                    "line_text": "Le soleil, en son vaste tour,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 33,
                    "line_text": "Ne voit qu'une famille immense,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 34,
                    "line_text": "Que devrait gouverner l'Amour.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 35,
                    "line_text": "Mortels, vous êtes tous des frères ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 36,
                    "line_text": "Jetez ces armes mercenaires :",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 37,
                    "line_text": "Que cherchez-vous dans les combats ?",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 38,
                    "line_text": "Quels biens poursuit votre imprudence ?",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "e"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 39,
                    "line_text": "En aurez-vous la jouissance",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "e"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 40,
                    "line_text": "Dans la triste nuit du trépas ?",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "De l'Inde aux bornes de la France,\nLe soleil, en son vaste tour,\nNe voit qu'une famille immense,\nQue devrait gouverner l'Amour.\nMortels, vous êtes tous des frères ;\nJetez ces armes mercenaires :\nQue cherchez-vous dans les combats ?\nQuels biens poursuit votre imprudence ?\nEn aurez-vous la jouissance\nDans la triste nuit du trépas ?"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 5,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 41,
                    "line_text": "Encor si pour votre patrie",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 42,
                    "line_text": "Vous saviez vous sacrifier !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 43,
                    "line_text": "Mais non ; vous vendez votre vie",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 44,
                    "line_text": "Aux mains qui daignent la payer.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 45,
                    "line_text": "Vous mourez pour la cause inique",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 46,
                    "line_text": "De quelque tyran politique",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 47,
                    "line_text": "Que vos yeux ne connaissent pas ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 48,
                    "line_text": "Et vous n'êtes, dans vos misères,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "e"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 49,
                    "line_text": "Que des assassins mercenaires",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "e"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 50,
                    "line_text": "Armés pour des maîtres ingrats.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Encor si pour votre patrie\nVous saviez vous sacrifier !\nMais non ; vous vendez votre vie\nAux mains qui daignent la payer.\nVous mourez pour la cause inique\nDe quelque tyran politique\nQue vos yeux ne connaissent pas ;\nEt vous n'êtes, dans vos misères,\nQue des assassins mercenaires\nArmés pour des maîtres ingrats."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 6,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 51,
                    "line_text": "Tels sont ces oiseaux de rapine,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 52,
                    "line_text": "Et ces animaux malfaisants,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 53,
                    "line_text": "Apprivoisés pour la ruine",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 54,
                    "line_text": "Des paisibles hôtes des champs :",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 55,
                    "line_text": "Aux sons d'un instrument sauvage,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 56,
                    "line_text": "Animés, ardents, pleins de rage,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 57,
                    "line_text": "Ils vont, d'un vol impétueux,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 58,
                    "line_text": "Sans choix, sans intérêt, sans gloire,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "e"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 59,
                    "line_text": "Saisir une folle victoire",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "e"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 60,
                    "line_text": "Dont le prix n'est jamais pour eux.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Tels sont ces oiseaux de rapine,\nEt ces animaux malfaisants,\nApprivoisés pour la ruine\nDes paisibles hôtes des champs :\nAux sons d'un instrument sauvage,\nAnimés, ardents, pleins de rage,\nIls vont, d'un vol impétueux,\nSans choix, sans intérêt, sans gloire,\nSaisir une folle victoire\nDont le prix n'est jamais pour eux."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 7,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 61,
                    "line_text": "O superbe, ô triste Italie !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 62,
                    "line_text": "Que tu plains ta fécondité !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 63,
                    "line_text": "Sous tes débris ensevelie,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 64,
                    "line_text": "Que tu déplores ta beauté !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 65,
                    "line_text": "Je vois tes moissons dévorées",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 66,
                    "line_text": "Par les nations conjurées",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 67,
                    "line_text": "Qui te flattaient de te venger :",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 68,
                    "line_text": "Faible, désolée, expirante,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "e"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 69,
                    "line_text": "Tu combats d'une main tremblante",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "e"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 70,
                    "line_text": "Pour le choix d'un maître étranger.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "O superbe, ô triste Italie !\nQue tu plains ta fécondité !\nSous tes débris ensevelie,\nQue tu déplores ta beauté !\nJe vois tes moissons dévorées\nPar les nations conjurées\nQui te flattaient de te venger :\nFaible, désolée, expirante,\nTu combats d'une main tremblante\nPour le choix d'un maître étranger."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 8,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 71,
                    "line_text": "Que toujours armés pour la guerre",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 72,
                    "line_text": "Nos rois soient les dieux de la paix ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 73,
                    "line_text": "Que leurs mains portent le tonnerre,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 74,
                    "line_text": "Sans se plaire à lancer ses traits.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 75,
                    "line_text": "Nous chérissons un berger sage,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 76,
                    "line_text": "Qui, dans un heureux pâturage,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 77,
                    "line_text": "Unit les troupeaux sous ses lois.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 78,
                    "line_text": "Malheur au pasteur sanguinaire",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "e"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 79,
                    "line_text": "Qui les expose en téméraire",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "e"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 80,
                    "line_text": "A la dent du tyran des bois !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Que toujours armés pour la guerre\nNos rois soient les dieux de la paix ;\nQue leurs mains portent le tonnerre,\nSans se plaire à lancer ses traits.\nNous chérissons un berger sage,\nQui, dans un heureux pâturage,\nUnit les troupeaux sous ses lois.\nMalheur au pasteur sanguinaire\nQui les expose en téméraire\nA la dent du tyran des bois !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 9,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 81,
                    "line_text": "Eh ! que m'importe la victoire",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 82,
                    "line_text": "D'un roi qui me perce le flanc,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 83,
                    "line_text": "D'un roi dont j'achète la gloire",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 84,
                    "line_text": "De ma fortune et de mon sang !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 85,
                    "line_text": "Quoi ! dans l'horreur de l'indigence,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 86,
                    "line_text": "Dans les langueurs, dans la souffrance,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 87,
                    "line_text": "Mes jours seront-ils plus sereins",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 88,
                    "line_text": "Quand on m'apprendra que nos princes",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "e"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 89,
                    "line_text": "Aux frontières de nos provinces",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "e"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 90,
                    "line_text": "Nagent dans le sang des Germains ?",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Eh ! que m'importe la victoire\nD'un roi qui me perce le flanc,\nD'un roi dont j'achète la gloire\nDe ma fortune et de mon sang !\nQuoi ! dans l'horreur de l'indigence,\nDans les langueurs, dans la souffrance,\nMes jours seront-ils plus sereins\nQuand on m'apprendra que nos princes\nAux frontières de nos provinces\nNagent dans le sang des Germains ?"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 10,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 91,
                    "line_text": "Colbert, toi qui dans ta patrie",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 92,
                    "line_text": "Amenas les arts et les jeux ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 93,
                    "line_text": "Colbert, ton heureuse industrie",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 94,
